{"title":"Hexo+Aurora+COS+CDN","uid":"50d103871956e893966b30af3d9ba8af","slug":"Hexo-Aurora-Cos-CDN","date":"9999-12-31T15:59:59.000Z","updated":"2022-02-14T09:26:52.776Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Hexo-Aurora-Cos-CDN.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<h1 id=\"Hexo-Aurora-COS-CDN\"><a href=\"#Hexo-Aurora-COS-CDN\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo+Aurora+COS+CDN\"></a>Hexo+Aurora+COS+CDN</h1><h2 id=\"Git安装\"><a href=\"#Git安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Git安装\"></a>Git安装</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Windows</p></blockquote>\n<p>访问官网</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-http\" data-language=\"http\"><code class=\"language-http\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;git-scm.com&#x2F;</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214145014.png\" alt=\"image-20220214145014802\"></p>\n<p>直接安装即可</p>\n<p><strong>若速度太慢可访问国内淘宝镜像</strong></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-http\" data-language=\"http\"><code class=\"language-http\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;registry.npmmirror.com&#x2F;binary.html?path&#x3D;git-for-windows&#x2F;</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214145150.png\" alt=\"image-20220214145150503\"></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Linux</p></blockquote>\n<p>本人使用版本为<code>Ubuntu 20.04</code>教程以此版本为例</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>首先确认系统是否已经安装Git</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">git</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214145327.png\" alt=\"image-20220214145327166\"></p>\n<p>出现上图则说明已安装Git可直接进入<code>Hexo安装</code></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>安装Git</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">apt install git</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>测试</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">git --version</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214145604.png\" alt=\"image-20220214145604170\"></p>\n</li>\n<li><p>配置</p>\n<ul>\n<li><p>user.name</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">git config --global user.name &#x3D; &quot;git提交用户名称&quot;</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>user.email</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">git config --global user.email &#x3D; &quot;你的email&quot;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p> 至此Git安装完成</p>\n<p>Hexo是前端化工程，所以需要Node依赖</p>\n<h2 id=\"Node-js安装\"><a href=\"#Node-js安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Node.js安装\"></a>Node.js安装</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Windows</p></blockquote>\n<ol>\n<li><p>官网下载安装包</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-http\" data-language=\"http\"><code class=\"language-http\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;nodejs.org&#x2F;zh-cn&#x2F;</code></pre></li>\n</ol>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214142813.png\" alt=\"image-20220214142806185\"></p>\n<p><strong>直接下一步、下一步安装即可</strong></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Linux</p></blockquote>\n<p>本人使用版本为<code>Ubuntu 20.04</code>教程以此版本为例</p>\n<ol>\n<li><p>更新apt源</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">apt update</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>安装</p>\n<p>本教程发布时Node官网稳定版为<code>16.14.0</code></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">curl -sL https:&#x2F;&#x2F;deb.nodesource.com&#x2F;setup_16.x | sudo -E bash -</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong>注意：</strong>如果你想安装其他版本只需在上面链接中修改 setup_16.x 为你想要的版本 例如：setup_12.x</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>获取</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo apt-get install -y nodejs</code></pre></li>\n<li><p>测试</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214143807.png\" alt=\"image-20220214143807851\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"Hexo安装\"><a href=\"#Hexo安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Hexo安装\"></a>Hexo安装</h2><h3 id=\"1、官网\"><a href=\"#1、官网\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1、官网\"></a>1、官网</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-http\" data-language=\"http\"><code class=\"language-http\">https:&#x2F;&#x2F;hexo.io&#x2F;zh-cn&#x2F;</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214143941.png\" alt=\"image-20220214143940944\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"2、安装\"><a href=\"#2、安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2、安装\"></a>2、安装</h3><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install hexo-cli -g</code></pre>\n\n<h3 id=\"3、初始化\"><a href=\"#3、初始化\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"3、初始化\"></a>3、初始化</h3><p>在你的工作空间执行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo init [项目名]</code></pre>\n\n<p>我这里为<code>hexoblog</code></p>\n<p>执行成功后进入目录</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214145906.png\" alt=\"image-20220214145906147\"></p>\n<p>目录结构与上图类似</p>\n<h3 id=\"4、测试\"><a href=\"#4、测试\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4、测试\"></a>4、测试</h3><p>在此目录下执行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo clean &amp; hexo g &amp; hexo s</code></pre>\n\n<ul>\n<li>hexo clean：  清理编译文件</li>\n<li>hexo g：编译项目</li>\n<li>hexo s(server) : 本地预览运行项目</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214144724.png\" alt=\"image-20220214144724615\"></p>\n<p>访问<code>http://localhost:4000</code>即可看到</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214145958.png\" alt=\"image-20220214145958471\"></p>\n<p>访问结果如上图则为安装成功</p>\n<h2 id=\"Aurora安装\"><a href=\"#Aurora安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Aurora安装\"></a>Aurora安装</h2><p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214150352.png\" alt=\"image-20220214150352273\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"1-安装\"><a href=\"#1-安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.安装\"></a>1.安装</h3><p>进入hexo初始化目录执行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install hexo-theme-aurora --save</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214150608.png\" alt=\"image-20220214150608776\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-配置\"><a href=\"#2-配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.配置\"></a>2.配置</h3><h4 id=\"2-1、创建配置文件\"><a href=\"#2-1、创建配置文件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1、创建配置文件\"></a>2.1、创建配置文件</h4><p>因为主题是使用 NPM 或者 Yarn 安装的，而不是 clone 到 themes 文件夹的。所以我们需要自己创建一个配置文件。你只需要在 Hexo 博客的根目录下创建一个 <code>_config.aurora.yml</code> 配置文件来配置主题。</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214150728.png\" alt=\"image-20220214150728558\"></p>\n<p>此时打开配置文件发现是空的我们可以到node_modules下找到hexo-theme-aurora</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214150921.png\" alt=\"image-20220214150921340\"></p>\n<p>在此目录下我们发现有一个_config.aurora.yml文件，我们可以复制此文件到hexo初始化根目录下</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214151350.png\" alt=\"image-20220214151349963\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"2-2、修改配置\"><a href=\"#2-2、修改配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.2、修改配置\"></a>2.2、修改配置</h4><p>打开_config.yml</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>修改路由方式</p></blockquote>\n<p>由于aurora是Vue3项目，所以我们要修改路由为Aurora支持的方式</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214151915.png\" alt=\"image-20220214151915098\"></p>\n<p>找到URL下的<code>permalink</code>改为<code>/post/:title.html</code></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>修改代码高亮模式</p></blockquote>\n<p>aurora主题是使用 <code>Prismjs</code> 来实现代码高亮显示，但 Hexo 默认是使用 <code>highlightjs</code>，因此你需要更改 Hexo 配置来使用 <code>Prismjs</code>:</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">highlight:\n  enable: false\n  line_number: true\n  auto_detect: false\n  tab_replace: &#39;&#39;\n  wrap: true\n  hljs: false\nprismjs:\n  enable: true\n  preprocess: true\n  line_number: true\n  tab_replace: &#39;&#39;</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"2-3、创建About页面\"><a href=\"#2-3、创建About页面\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.3、创建About页面\"></a>2.3、创建About页面</h4><p>主题默认开启了 <code>about</code> 页面，所以我们需要创建这个 about 页，要不主题就无法正常显示 about 页。</p>\n<p>要创建这个默认的 about 页，只需要执行这个 <code>Hexo 的命令</code>：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo new page about</code></pre>\n\n<p>执行完毕后，你会发现在 <code>source/</code> 文件中多处了一个新的文件夹：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sh\" data-language=\"sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">.\n└── source\n    └── about\n        └── index.md</code></pre>\n\n<p>你可以随意修改这个 <code>index.md</code> markdown 文件中的内容，此文件的内容将会现在在我们的 about 页面中。</p>\n<p>重新运行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-sh\" data-language=\"sh\"><code class=\"language-sh\">hexo clean &amp; hexo g &amp; hexo server</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214153036.png\" alt=\"image-20220214153035925\"></p>\n<p>此时aurora主题已安装完成</p>\n<h2 id=\"COS部署\"><a href=\"#COS部署\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"COS部署\"></a>COS部署</h2><h3 id=\"1-开通对象存储\"><a href=\"#1-开通对象存储\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.开通对象存储\"></a>1.开通对象存储</h3><p>注册腾讯云账号并登录</p>\n<h4 id=\"1-1-搜索对象存储\"><a href=\"#1-1-搜索对象存储\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.1 .搜索对象存储\"></a>1.1 .搜索对象存储</h4><p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214160353.png\" alt=\"image-20220214160353277\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"1-2-创建存储桶\"><a href=\"#1-2-创建存储桶\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.2.创建存储桶\"></a>1.2.创建存储桶</h4><p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214160633.png\" alt=\"image-20220214160633648\"></p>\n<p><strong>注意：</strong> 有些地区存储桶不支持CDN建议选择<code>上海</code></p>\n<p>点击下一步</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214160740.png\" alt=\"image-20220214160740884\"></p>\n<p>这里不用选直接下一步</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214162838.png\" alt=\"image-20220214162838582\"></p>\n<p>点击创建即可</p>\n<h4 id=\"1-3-开启静态网站\"><a href=\"#1-3-开启静态网站\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.3.开启静态网站\"></a>1.3.开启静态网站</h4><p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214161044.png\" alt=\"image-20220214161044670\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-部署Hexo到COS\"><a href=\"#2-部署Hexo到COS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.部署Hexo到COS\"></a>2.部署Hexo到COS</h3><h4 id=\"2-1-获取COS秘钥\"><a href=\"#2-1-获取COS秘钥\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1.获取COS秘钥\"></a>2.1.获取COS秘钥</h4><p>获取<code>APPID</code>，<code>SecretId</code>，<code>SecretKey</code>，<code>Bucket</code>，<code>Region</code>这五个参数</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214161743.png\" alt=\"image-20220214161743435\"></p>\n<p>新建秘钥</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214161812.png\" alt=\"image-20220214161812764\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"2-2-安装博客推送插件\"><a href=\"#2-2-安装博客推送插件\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.2.安装博客推送插件\"></a>2.2.安装博客推送插件</h4><p><code>hexo-deployer-cos-cdn</code></p>\n<p>到Hexo根目录下执行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">npm install hexo-deployer-cos-cdn --save</code></pre>\n\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214163058.png\" alt=\"image-20220214163058144\"></p>\n<p>执行完成即可</p>\n<h4 id=\"2-3-配置\"><a href=\"#2-3-配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.3.配置\"></a>2.3.配置</h4><p>打开_config.yml文件</p>\n<p>配置deploy</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214162353.png\" alt=\"image-20220214162353456\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-yaml\" data-language=\"yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\">deploy:\n  # tencent cos-cdn\n- type: cos-cdn\n  cloud: tencent\n  appId: 123456789 # 这里填写刚才新建立的秘钥的appid\n  secretId: abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz # 这里填写secretId\n  secretKey: abcdefghijklmnopqrstuvwxyz # 这里填写secretKey\n  bucket: hexo-blog-123456789 # 这里是存储桶名称\n  region: ap-shanghai # 这里是存储桶所属地区</code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"2-4-编译推送\"><a href=\"#2-4-编译推送\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.4. 编译推送\"></a>2.4. 编译推送</h4><p>执行</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">hexo g -d</code></pre>\n\n<p>结果</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214164454.png\" alt=\"image-20220214164454292\"></p>\n<p><code>注意：此操作会刷新CDN缓存 不必手动刷新</code></p>\n<h4 id=\"2-5-查看\"><a href=\"#2-5-查看\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.5. 查看\"></a>2.5. 查看</h4><p>到存储桶里查看</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214164552.png\" alt=\"image-20220214164552125\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214164734.png\" alt=\"image-20220214164734548\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214164817.png\" alt=\"image-20220214164817568\"></p>\n<p>成功！</p>\n<h2 id=\"CDN加速\"><a href=\"#CDN加速\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CDN加速\"></a>CDN加速</h2><p>打开存储桶设置</p>\n<h3 id=\"1-默认cdn加速\"><a href=\"#1-默认cdn加速\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"1.默认cdn加速\"></a>1.默认cdn加速</h3><p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214165244.png\" alt=\"image-20220214165244019\"></p>\n<p>源站类型选择 <code>静态网站源站</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"2-自定义域名加速\"><a href=\"#2-自定义域名加速\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.自定义域名加速\"></a>2.自定义域名加速</h3><h4 id=\"2-1开启自定义域名加速\"><a href=\"#2-1开启自定义域名加速\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.1开启自定义域名加速\"></a>2.1开启自定义域名加速</h4><p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214165526.png\" alt=\"image-20220214165526077\"></p>\n<h4 id=\"2-2-域名解析\"><a href=\"#2-2-域名解析\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"2.2 域名解析\"></a>2.2 域名解析</h4><p><img src=\"https://gitee.com/zniceya/picgo/raw/master/image/20220214165728.png\" alt=\"image-20220214165728612\"></p>\n<p>记录值为cdn加速CNAME</p>\n<h4 id=\"2-3-修改CD